Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:16.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri martial artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:23.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:27.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\an8\fs32\fade(770,0)}Karakuri Kengouden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fade(770,0)}Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:33.18,TitleOP,en,0,0,40,,{\fs24\fade(770,0)}(The Story of {\i1}Karakuri{\i0} Martial Artist: Road of Musashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:38.02,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A man always dreams of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.77,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,in the center of the world to become
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.65,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,AH! AH! the strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:49.70,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the sword of your heart high to the wide sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.33,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the curtain to the road of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.92,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A skilled swordsman roams on Jipangu State
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:06.55,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His name is Musashi, a Karakuri man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:08.05,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Go! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:10.97,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.80,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:19.27,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Battles of yesterdays make you stronger today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:25.52,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.44,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.99,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.49,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes life dazzling
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.58,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:45.84,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:51.09,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:05.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Once being rough in the Miyamoto village in mountains, Musashi was punished
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:11.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,by Takuan, but Otsuru rescued him and Musashi went to train himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,He met Kojirō who will become his rival of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,and he was completely defeated without mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dark clouds were in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:28.46,TitleEP,en,0,0,230,,Training in Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:28.46,TitleEP,en,0,0,110,,Makes Me Hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,This place is Okayamāna castle town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:43.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've heard about this place, but I never thought this place would be so lively-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:06.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a beautiful kimono! I want to have Otsuru wear one-{\i0}dasu{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:26.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything here was rightfully surprising to country-bred Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:35.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Aren't these pomegranates from Matsukasi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:39.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,2 mons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,2 mons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Pay the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Price?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,I hope you wouldn't say you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,I know what a price is-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then pay the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why would I-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is for sale! It is obvious that you have to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,There are pomegranates everywhere in my Miyamoto village, and thus are free-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Paying for such thing is something to laugh about-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:16.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Too bad for ya, but you are not at Miyamoto village! Now, give me the money or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! Where are you, thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:36.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,What do you mean, to call this Musashi who will be the number one martial artist of Jipangu a thief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,That voice must be a scream from a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is not manly to not go rescue her right now-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mister! Consider yourself lucky to have your head intact-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's a relief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! You still gotta pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:05:00.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,The one surrounded by martial artists was a girl resembling Nishida Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Miss, would you like to have a tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Have a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,How about a drive on my wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:19.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,The future number one martial artist of Jipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,From Miyamaoto village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Musashi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Aren't you interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,You might get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're going to be hurt-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thanks! Thank you! Thank you so much-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:10.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Those martial artists are from Yoshioka Dōjō.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yoshioka Dōjō?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:17.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a Dōjō in Miyako with the strongest martial artists in Jipangu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:17.07,Note,en,0,0,0,,(Miyako: the capital)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Strongest in Jipangu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,A branch has opened recently at this castle town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everyone tremble all over only by saying that one's a member of Yoshioka clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:29.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,They act as if everything is theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:34.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,But as long as Musashi's here, no need to fear-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:41.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't let your guards down. Your opponent were mere beginners; there are lots of strong people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:47.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to worry! Until now, I only lost a battle once-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi really sounds like a name that I can depend on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:54.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can eat this! These are be the best dangos you will ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whoa, these dangos really look tasty-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,That dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will you be able to eat it alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.33,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,70,,Sējūrō
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Tell your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Tell me your name first if you want to know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Yoshioka. Yoshioka Sējūrō!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yoshioka Sējūrō!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:36.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,He is our master who is a son of the master of Yoshioka clan from Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:43.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,He took the trouble for the first time ever since the Yoshioka Dōjō branch here opened to issue a warning from himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Musashi from Miyamoto village-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,So what's your business-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:54.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,I heard that our young students were attacked, so I came to show how things will work around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? That's a honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,So what's your payment-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Manju?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Red bean paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Castella?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:05.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,My wooden sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:49.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn you! Damn you! Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's a back side of my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's our master Sējūrō!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:15.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph. He wasted my time with his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:29.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thus there is no way to let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:34.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,A man like this should disappear for the world as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,How refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:51.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:57.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh my, if you get all heated up, you'll end up making all that pee evaporate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:57.24,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,80,,Bokuden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:01.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,How dare... You're going down first! Get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:05.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wha... what the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:28.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's that? Should I take my sword out, you will not stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mutōdori{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.79,Note,en,0,0,0,,({\i1}Mutōdori{\i0}: 無刀取り. Defeating opponent with sword without using one)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:58.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,You should take a short nap too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:07.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was a nice stretch to wake me up. Thank you for the service.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:12.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,W- wait for a moment. You seem to be a famed martial artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm just a plain old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Name, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bokuden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,The one to be called a master swordsman, Tsukahara Bokuden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:34.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's that Tsukahara Bokuden! It looks like he's full of weak points, but he got none!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bokuden...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:58.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going by following Bokuden, Musashi? Wait for the stormy latter half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey there! Can't you hear me asking you to stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,You've dropped your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please accept me as your student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:25.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you give me back the money I dropped, I'll take you as a student... not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop! {\i1}Baka{\i0}den!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:30.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, now! I am Bokuden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take me as your student!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Raising students isn't my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,My thing is to be a student-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:44.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Make... me... your... student...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Following Bokuden for 3,000 {\i1}ri{\i0}s,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.93,Note,en,0,0,0,,(3,000 {\i1}ri{\i0} ≒ 11,781 km ≒ 7,320 mi.)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:53.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,well, not that much, but anyway, Musashi stubbornly kept following.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:15.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Once decided, stake my life. It is the way of Musashi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong? Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Another dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Another dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Another dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:35.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Another dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Another dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,I beg of you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:46.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything you've done considered, I don't really have a choice, do I? I will take you a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,But! The training will be painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Aren't all trainings painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,To become the number one martial artist of Jipangu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:59.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll do my best for any training no matter how painful it is - in water or in fire-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:05.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it? No matter what kind of opponent is, I'll hit him hard and make him fly... over the cloud-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musashi! You're a student of Tsukahara Bokuden now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pray for you to open your eyes and become a good rival of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Keep your waist straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:42.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,The most important thing when yielding a sword is to use your waist to cleave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you understand, Musashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,Body training is what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mental training will raise your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:15:01.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gut means the spiritual strength of not getting perplexed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:06.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,To raise your guts, you must understand the nature and train your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:07.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,To defeat an opponent, your feet must be as quick as your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes to run away is to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course your body also has to become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ten years early, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Focus, Musashi. The most essential elements of real-life training are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,"Sight" first, "foot" second, "guts" third, and "force" fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,You've already learned "force", "guts", and "foot".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:56.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,"Sight" here means to see. To see your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,There are two kinds of sight: sight of eyes, and sight of swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:04.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sight of eye means intuition; sight of sword means to observe the phenomenon of objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:14.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm teaching you even using my dinner time and you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,You even ate my dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:08.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job, Musashi. From today we will go to the second step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:08.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's bothering you, Otsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:32.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master... I have something I must apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,About letting Musashi run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:37.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You did a good job, Otsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:45.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,I was thinking that it was time to let him go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:55.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,I could have forgiven him, but your compassion serves better as an everlasting lesson for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything will turn out well for Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:02.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder what's Musashi doing at where.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,But no need to worry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:12.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's Musashi after all. He'll bravely fight for his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.27,Default,en,0,0,0,L1823,Soft and naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.14,Default,en,0,0,0,L1846,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:51.99,Default,en,0,0,0,L1850,What are you doing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.95,Default,en,0,0,0,L1852,You idiot! Do you think your opponent is going to save you in real battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:24.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:32.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musashi! Get a grip! Do you want to die at such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:33.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:40.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Musashi! To drop dead at such a place, you truly were a waste of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:42.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.85,Default,en,0,0,0,L2014,He was a fine guy, to keep onto his sword to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.75,Default,en,0,0,0,L2018,Chink in the armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job, Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:57.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, it's time for you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Winds of era is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! You shall go to Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,To Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:12.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have nothing more to teach. I taught everything I know to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,For the rest, Musashi, you shall hone yourself with your own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Can you do it, Musashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:21.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:29.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! First, become the number one martial artist of Jipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:35.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Lastly, do not forget the ultimate purpose of a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,To win without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,To win without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:44.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Go, Musashi! For the future of Jipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,It will be a problem if I get tired over my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:07.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Still, he was an interesting guy with good guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:16.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,With a high ambition, he heads to Miyako! What will be waiting for him? A flower, or a storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:24.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,That does not matter! Go forward, Musashi! Dive into flowers and storms! That's the path of swordsmanship of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.55,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.81,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.18,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.81,0:22:52.81,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:58.15,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:01.74,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.16,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:14.25,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:22.30,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:27.01,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:37.94,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:46.41,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:52.24,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:08.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,After a harsh training, I became stronger and now I'm heading for the Miyako Palace-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:13.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wow, it sure is a big city, and there sure are lots of weird guys-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:21.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,In front of a giant fighter whose hobby is collecting thousands swords, some child-looking guy appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:24.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next episode: Benkei at the Capital Castle City-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:27.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,It will pierce through your eyes-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:31.24,NoteOnAnime,en,60,0,60,,{\an7}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:31.24,TitleEP,en,0,0,80,,Benkei at the Capital Castle City
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:31.24,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!